Project Name: Spatio-Temporal Image Encoding

Description: This project represents the implementation of the Spatio-Temporal Image Encoding used in the paper "Human Activity Recognition: A Spatio-temporal Image Encoding of 3D Skeleton Data for Online Action Detection" published in the "International Joint Conference on Computer Vision, Imaging and Computer Graphics Theory and Applications(VISAPP) 2022".

Author: Nassim Mokhtari, Alexis Nédélec and Pierre De Loor.

Project URL: https://www.scitepress.org/PublicationsDetail.aspx?ID=rsbxRj6Ic2Y=&t=1

This project is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. See the LICENSE file for more information about the terms of the license.
